Hey guys quick map I made in about 10 hours since i somewhat gave up on the map ive been working on all week. I think its the most fun map i've made so far so hopefully you guys think the same. Also, i had alot of trouble with packing for some reason so if anything is missing please tell me. I tested it though and im pretty sure i got it all.
